OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Ccharged with National Security Act
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThree Iranian men living in London
OL,8,Fhave been charged with offences under
OL,9,Fthe National Security Act following an
OL,10,Finvestigation by counter terror police.
OL,12,FMostafa Sepahvand, 39, of St John's
OL,13,FWood, Farhad Javadi Manesh, 44, of
OL,14,FKensal Rise, and Shapoor Qalehali
OL,15,FKhani Noori, 55, of Ealing, are due to
OL,16,Fappear at Westminster Magistrate's
OL,17,FCourt on Saturday.
