OL,3,CThree Iranian men living in London
OL,4,Ccharged with National Security Act
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThey were arrested on May 3 under
OL,8,FSection 27 of the National Security
OL,9,FAct and all three were charged with
OL,10,Fengaging in conduct likely to assist
OL,11,Fthe Iranian foreign intelligence
OL,12,Fservice between August 14 2024 and
OL,13,FFebruary 16 2025.
OL,15,FSepahvand was also charged with
OL,16,Fengaging in surveillance,
OL,17,Freconnaissance and open-source
OL,18,Fresearch, intending to commit acts,
OL,19,Fnamely serious violence against a
OL,20,Fperson in the UK.
