OL,7,FCommander Dominic Murphy, from the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police's Counter
OL,9,FTerrorism Command, said: "These are
OL,10,Fextremely serious charges under the
OL,11,FNational Security Act, which have come
OL,12,Fabout following what has been a very
OL,13,Fcomplex and fast-moving investigation.
OL,15,F"Since the men were arrested two weeks
OL,16,Fago, detectives have been working
OL,17,Faround the clock and we have worked
OL,18,Fclosely with colleagues in the CPS to
OL,19,Freach this point.
