OL,7,F"We have been in contact with the
OL,8,Findividuals directly affected, and we
OL,9,Fcontinue to provide them with support.
OL,11,F"Now that these men have been charged
OL,12,FI would urge people not to speculate
OL,13,Fabout this case, so that the criminal
OL,14,Fjustice process can run its course."
OL,16,FA fourth man, arrested on May 9 as
OL,17,Fpart of the investigation, was
OL,18,Freleased without charge on Thursday,
OL,19,FMay 15.
